This is my personal vim environment.

Plugins:   
ctags		: sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags
taglist 	: clone from https://github.com/vim-scripts/taglist.vim
minibufexpl  	: clone from https://github.com/fholgado/minibufexpl.vim.git
winmanager	: clone from https://github.com/vim-scripts/winmanager.git
a.vim		: clone from https://github.com/vim-scripts/a.vim
The nerd-tree   : clone from https://github.com/vim-scripts/The-NERD-tree.git
neocomplcache   : clone from https://github.com/vim-scripts/neocomplcache.git

colors: clone from https://github.com/nono/github_vim_theme.git


read more:
ctags : generate tags on source code
taglist: show tags on vim window
minibufexpl: show little screen windows
winmanager: make vim like windows 
a.vim	:  switch header and source code
colors:   githu style colorscheme
neocomplcache: word auto completion





